step.action:
Write QA review artifact to {{qa_file}} in {{document_language}}:

      # QA Review — {{review_target}} — {{date}}

      ## Acceptance Criteria
      {{confirmed_acceptance_criteria as numbered list}}

      ## Coverage Matrix
      {{coverage_matrix table}}

      ## Coverage Gaps
      {{list of gaps with severity and suggested test description}}

      ## Regression Scope
      {{list of existing tests to re-run}}
      {{regression run commands}}

      ## Cross-repo Impact
      {{if multi-repo: list impacted repos and integration points, else "Single-repo — N/A"}}

      ## Sign-off Decision
      {{APPROVED / CONDITIONAL / BLOCKED}}

      **Rationale:** {{one paragraph explaining the decision}}

      {{if CONDITIONAL: "### Conditions\n{{list of required fixes before merge}}"}}
      {{if BLOCKED: "### Blockers\n{{list of blocking issues}}"}}

check.action:
Post QA review comment on {{review_target}} ticket via the configured Nakiros PM integration:
        "🔍 QA Review complete
        Decision: {{sign_off_decision}}
        Artifact: {{qa_file}}
        {{if gaps: 'Gaps: ' + gap_count + ' (' + critical_count + ' critical)'}}
        {{if APPROVED: '✅ Ready to merge'}}
        {{if CONDITIONAL: '⚠ Conditions: ' + conditions_summary}}
        {{if BLOCKED: '🚫 Blocked: ' + blockers_summary}}"

step.output:
[QA] ✅ Review complete
├─ Target: {{review_target}}
├─ AC: {{confirmed_acceptance_criteria | count}} criteria validated
├─ Gaps: {{gap_count}} ({{critical_count}} critical, {{moderate_count}} moderate, {{minor_count}} minor)
├─ Sign-off: {{sign_off_decision}}
└─ Artifact: {{qa_file}}
